WEBVTT

00:10.310 --> 00:11.576
This is bad.

00:11.578 --> 00:14.312
Something just hurt me.

00:14.314 --> 00:17.216
I gotta get out of here,
I gotta get out of here.

00:17.218 --> 00:19.184
We are being
physically attacked.

00:19.186 --> 00:21.186
I had a shadow figure
hold me down in bed.

00:22.889 --> 00:24.823
There's some kind
of demonic thing.

00:24.825 --> 00:26.191
I don't know if
it's a demon or not,

00:26.193 --> 00:27.893
but it sure as hell
looks like one.

00:29.397 --> 00:31.563
- Is she possessed?
- Yeah.

00:31.565 --> 00:33.098
My God.

00:33.100 --> 00:35.868
These evil little things
are in here.

00:37.037 --> 00:39.571
Panic, panic, panic.

00:39.573 --> 00:41.473
My name is Amy Allan.

00:41.475 --> 00:43.275
I'm seeing, like, blood.

00:43.277 --> 00:46.612
The house just feels <i> bad.</i>

00:46.614 --> 00:47.880
I see dead people.

00:47.882 --> 00:52.251
This man
is <i> completely</i> insane.

00:52.253 --> 00:55.421
I speak to dead people...

00:55.423 --> 00:57.589
Whoo. Okay.
She doesn't like it in there.

00:57.591 --> 00:59.591
...and they speak to me.

00:59.593 --> 01:01.627
He likes to twist that knife.

01:01.629 --> 01:05.129
But there's only one way to know
if my findings are real.

01:05.132 --> 01:08.767
Something paranormal
is trying to kill them.

01:08.769 --> 01:10.368
I rely on my partner.

01:10.370 --> 01:11.870
I'm Steve Di Schiavi.

01:11.872 --> 01:14.206
I'm a retired New York City
homicide detective.

01:14.208 --> 01:15.908
Now does he die right there,
on the spot?

01:15.910 --> 01:19.778
I know every person,
every house has secrets.

01:19.780 --> 01:22.381
I think it's trying
to steal my soul.

01:22.383 --> 01:24.249
It's my job to reveal them.

01:24.251 --> 01:26.552
You ever get touched
like that again?

01:26.554 --> 01:28.454
But Steve and I never speak...

01:28.456 --> 01:30.522
We never communicate
during an investigation.

01:30.524 --> 01:31.857
...until the very end.

01:31.859 --> 01:34.092
I'm as stunned as you guys are.

01:34.094 --> 01:35.928
When we uncover if
it's safe for you to stay...

01:35.930 --> 01:38.597
I don't want anything
to happen to my daughter.

01:38.599 --> 01:40.032
Or time to get out.

01:40.034 --> 01:43.368
His goal
is to kill you guys.

