01:55.683 --> 01:57.148
I'm in Mahwah, New Jersey.

01:57.150 --> 02:00.385
It's a suburb about 45 minutes
northwest of New York City.

02:00.387 --> 02:03.989
I got a call from a mother
named Jen. Sounded really bad.

02:03.991 --> 02:05.357
She says something in her house

02:05.359 --> 02:07.626
is attacking her
and her four kids.

02:07.628 --> 02:09.026
And if Amy and I can't help,

02:09.029 --> 02:11.029
somebody's gonna
get seriously hurt.

02:14.834 --> 02:16.969
Before Amy arrives,
I sweep the house

02:16.971 --> 02:19.037
for any leading information.

02:20.374 --> 02:23.041
Family photographs
and religious symbols

02:23.043 --> 02:24.843
can influence her findings,

02:24.845 --> 02:27.346
so it's important I cover
or remove them all.

02:29.850 --> 02:31.383
When I'm done,

02:31.385 --> 02:34.052
the location will be ready
for tonight's walk.

02:45.465 --> 02:47.966
This place is not good.

02:51.138 --> 02:54.139
I'm just getting feelings
in here, like, emotions.

02:54.141 --> 02:57.709
Unsettled, nervous,
worried, stress.

02:59.046 --> 03:01.079
Like, I'm hearing like,
"Get away from me.

03:01.081 --> 03:02.747
Like, "get away, get away,
get away."

03:02.749 --> 03:06.018
This is really bad. I wanna
run away. I don't like this.

03:18.031 --> 03:19.230
Well, Jen,
I'm glad I'm here,

03:19.232 --> 03:20.499
'cause when we spoke
on the phone,

03:20.501 --> 03:22.267
you sounded pretty upset.
The hell's going on here?

03:22.269 --> 03:24.236
I feel like
I'm living in hell.

03:24.238 --> 03:26.638
The activity is
aggressive in this house,

03:26.640 --> 03:29.641
and it's going after
me and my kids.

03:29.643 --> 03:32.777
Afraid, you know, something's
gonna happen to one of us.

03:32.779 --> 03:35.380
And I can't do that as a mother.
I need your help.

03:35.382 --> 03:37.516
Well, that's why
I'm here, honey.
I know.

03:38.852 --> 03:40.652
So, Jen, who exactly
lives in the house?

03:40.654 --> 03:43.187
My husband Gary
and my four kids.

03:43.189 --> 03:45.289
This is Joe. He's 15.

03:45.291 --> 03:48.193
These are my twins,
Ryan and Michael. They're 13.

03:48.195 --> 03:49.461
Okay.

03:49.463 --> 03:51.263
And this is my daughter
Samantha, and she's 6.

03:51.265 --> 03:53.398
Jen, do me a favor.
Give me a -- gimme a list

03:53.400 --> 03:55.100
of what you guys
are experiencing here.

03:55.102 --> 03:58.070
Hearing disembodied voices.

03:58.072 --> 04:01.172
There's been
a lot of shadow figures.

04:01.174 --> 04:04.109
Objects moving on their own.

04:04.111 --> 04:07.345
The health of the family
is declining.

04:07.347 --> 04:09.948
We are being
physically attacked.

04:09.950 --> 04:13.151
Okay. So now, Jen, is everybody
being affected by this?

04:13.153 --> 04:15.820
Yeah, but Joseph is getting
the brunt of it.

04:15.822 --> 04:18.156
- In what way?
- He's lashing out.

04:18.158 --> 04:20.825
He's doing things that are not
in character for him.

04:20.827 --> 04:23.161
It's not
normal teenage stuff.

04:23.163 --> 04:24.896
Well, what do you think
is here, honey?

04:24.898 --> 04:27.832
I believe there's some kind
of hold or possession on him.

04:27.834 --> 04:29.234
What do you think it wants?

04:29.236 --> 04:30.736
I'm afraid it wants
to kill him.

04:32.539 --> 04:34.840
You got a lot on your shoulders
as a mom to begin with.

04:34.842 --> 04:36.574
How are dealing with
all this other stuff?

04:36.576 --> 04:39.444
I have horrible anxiety.

04:39.446 --> 04:42.080
And I just can't
protect my kids.

04:42.082 --> 04:43.715
Samantha's only 6.

04:45.051 --> 04:47.985
And she --
she's a baby still.

04:47.987 --> 04:49.254
I don't wanna live
like this anymore.

04:51.959 --> 04:54.192
I'm seeing a male out here.

04:54.194 --> 04:56.728
And this person
is, like, confused

04:56.730 --> 04:59.731
and, like, scared,
pacing or running.

05:04.405 --> 05:07.205
The dude from outside
comes in here.

05:07.207 --> 05:09.074
And he's running
and he's running.

05:10.477 --> 05:11.843
Boom, and then he's in here.

05:13.047 --> 05:15.280
Also, he makes the living
feel anxious

05:15.282 --> 05:17.516
and it almost makes you
wanna throw up.

05:17.518 --> 05:19.084
Just utter despair.

05:19.086 --> 05:22.353
And your stomach drops out
and you wanna vomit.

05:22.355 --> 05:24.822
Definitely getting the chills
with him.

05:24.824 --> 05:27.726
He affects electrical stuff.

05:27.728 --> 05:29.328
He has too much energy.

05:30.397 --> 05:32.029
How would the living
perceive this?

05:32.031 --> 05:34.766
People do see
a dark shadow moving by.

05:34.768 --> 05:37.703
He's just a shadow person
down here.

05:45.612 --> 05:47.445
Okay, Jen, so what's
going on in this room?

05:47.447 --> 05:50.515
Constantly,
we see shadow figures

05:50.517 --> 05:52.484
coming down the stairs.

05:52.486 --> 05:55.387
I could be in bed and see them
from my bedroom, too.

05:55.389 --> 05:58.390
So is this the only spot that
you see the shadow figures?

05:58.392 --> 06:00.926
No, I see them
all over the house.

06:00.928 --> 06:05.163
I see shadow figures
outside behind the fence.

06:05.165 --> 06:07.332
This one is completely tall.

06:07.334 --> 06:09.734
It's like he has got,
like, an overcoat on.

06:09.736 --> 06:12.537
I think that this guy
is no good.

06:12.539 --> 06:15.207
Okay.
Anything else strange happen?

06:15.209 --> 06:17.375
On top of the stairs,
all the sudden,

06:17.377 --> 06:19.744
I felt a hand on my back
and I got pushed,

06:19.746 --> 06:22.580
and, like, it was gonna, like,
throw me down the stairs.

06:22.582 --> 06:24.750
So how hard did you get pushed?
Just gimme an idea.

06:24.752 --> 06:26.417
I mean, like this.

06:26.419 --> 06:29.087
Okay, you're getting shoved,
and you have a 6-year-old.

06:29.089 --> 06:30.822
Who's to say that
can't happen to her?

06:30.824 --> 06:33.158
That's my concern.
He wants to hurt us.

06:36.196 --> 06:39.164
This guy's energy
is so bad.

06:39.166 --> 06:40.999
Like, I don't even wanna
go down the stairs right now

06:41.001 --> 06:45.537
'cause little...
a little loopy.

06:47.040 --> 06:49.841
I'm not feeling very well
right now.

06:49.843 --> 06:54.745
I think that dude from outside
is making me feel sick.

06:54.747 --> 06:56.248
I feel drained.

06:56.250 --> 06:58.550
I feel nauseous.

06:58.552 --> 07:00.118
I feel very dizzy.

07:01.855 --> 07:05.223
I would be worried about
the living accidentally falling.

07:07.060 --> 07:10.061
He is doing things

07:10.063 --> 07:11.863
because he's angry.

07:11.865 --> 07:14.065
Any idea what kind of affect
he might have on the living?

07:14.067 --> 07:15.934
I think that
they would feel a drain.

07:15.936 --> 07:19.371
I think they would feel, like,
sudden exhaustion.

07:19.373 --> 07:22.073
I think that
they feel uncomfortable.

07:22.075 --> 07:24.209
I think, panicked.

07:31.752 --> 07:33.151
So what's going on in here?

07:33.153 --> 07:37.555
I think whatever is in this
house is draining my energy.

07:37.557 --> 07:39.724
- Okay.
- I can't sleep at night.

07:39.726 --> 07:41.726
And then I can't wake up
in the morning.

07:41.728 --> 07:43.294
All right, anything else
like that?

07:43.296 --> 07:46.131
My health is declining.
I'm sore.

07:46.133 --> 07:48.032
I get fevers on and off.

07:48.034 --> 07:51.303
Everything in my body,
every muscle, everything.

07:51.305 --> 07:52.970
So what makes you think
this is paranormal?

07:52.972 --> 07:54.706
Medically, they can't
find anything wrong.

07:54.708 --> 07:55.907
All right, anything else?

07:55.909 --> 07:58.676
There's mood changes,
me and my husband.

07:58.678 --> 08:02.914
He seems to be
more of a nasty, mad,

08:02.916 --> 08:06.651
taking out aggression
and things like that.

08:06.653 --> 08:08.987
When I'm here,
I'm not normal either.

08:08.989 --> 08:10.689
You know,
we fight constantly.

08:10.691 --> 08:11.756
Well, I gotta
be honest with you.

08:11.758 --> 08:12.991
I gotta play
devil's advocate here.

08:12.993 --> 08:15.927
- I mean, couples fight.
- It's not normal fights.

08:15.929 --> 08:17.128
We're like soul mates.

08:17.130 --> 08:19.130
We've been through
a lot of things together.

08:19.132 --> 08:21.066
This should not
break us up.

08:21.068 --> 08:22.767
I'm afraid to even ask.
Anything else?

08:22.769 --> 08:25.403
I've been bruised
in the middle of the night.

08:25.405 --> 08:27.939
I wake up with them.
It just makes no sense.

08:27.941 --> 08:29.207
So what kinda bruises
we talking about?

08:29.209 --> 08:31.209
Like three fingerprints?

08:31.211 --> 08:32.943
How do you know your husband's
not rolling over

08:32.946 --> 08:34.212
and banging into you?

08:34.214 --> 08:37.249
Well, he sleeps like a rock,
and there's no way.

08:42.355 --> 08:44.155
So I'm seeing
this older woman,

08:44.157 --> 08:46.691
and she's, like,
hurting living people.

08:48.295 --> 08:52.764
I'm seeing that older woman
trying to strangle somebody.

08:56.202 --> 09:00.371
The living here are absolutely
experiencing a lot of pain.

09:00.373 --> 09:03.908
She died from an infection
or something.

09:03.910 --> 09:05.943
I don't know if somebody
keeps getting, like,

09:05.945 --> 09:07.646
some kind of infections
all the time.

09:09.583 --> 09:12.183
She's, like, cutting people.

09:12.185 --> 09:14.185
I see her putting on nails.

09:14.187 --> 09:16.655
And I see her touching
a baby's belly,

09:16.657 --> 09:19.057
and that makes me nervous.

09:19.059 --> 09:21.326
Why is this woman
doing this?

09:21.328 --> 09:22.761
She wants the living
out of here

09:22.763 --> 09:26.731
because she feels
they brought the evil in.

09:26.733 --> 09:29.266
"Get them out. Get them out."

09:46.136 --> 09:47.836
So, Gary, I was talking
to your wife earlier,

09:47.838 --> 09:49.537
and she was saying that
whatever's in this house

09:49.539 --> 09:50.905
is going after her
and your kids.

09:50.907 --> 09:52.340
I mean, you agree with that?

09:52.342 --> 09:53.741
It definitely appears
that way.

09:53.743 --> 09:56.144
She seems to have had
every paranormal experience

09:56.146 --> 09:57.946
she can have under the sun.

09:57.948 --> 10:00.348
Now what about you?
Have you had anything?

10:00.350 --> 10:02.083
Well, we have
a lot of issues

10:02.085 --> 10:04.218
with our electronics
and electrical systems.

10:04.220 --> 10:06.554
You know, lights turning on
when there's nobody there.

10:06.556 --> 10:08.289
Televisions coming back on

10:08.291 --> 10:10.091
when there's no one there
to turn them on.

10:10.093 --> 10:12.493
Then to have something
just plugged in

10:12.495 --> 10:15.696
just to start smoking and burst
into flames for no reason?

10:15.698 --> 10:16.965
I don't know
how to explain that.

10:16.967 --> 10:18.566
Is there an issue with
the electrical here or...

10:18.568 --> 10:20.168
No, all the electrical
has been upgraded,

10:20.170 --> 10:22.470
from the panel
right to the fixtures.

10:22.472 --> 10:24.305
Okay. Anything else?

10:24.307 --> 10:27.442
One night, I had a shadow figure
come and hold me down in bed.

10:29.045 --> 10:30.512
And what'd you do?

10:30.514 --> 10:31.979
I was kinda, like, frozen,

10:31.981 --> 10:33.548
couldn't say anything,
couldn't do anything

10:33.550 --> 10:36.184
and I just kinda laid there
for a minute or so,

10:36.186 --> 10:39.854
and that I felt it just
lift up the pressure off me

10:39.856 --> 10:42.757
and it left the room.
- Wow.

10:42.759 --> 10:44.091
So now your wife
also mentioned to me

10:44.093 --> 10:45.860
she sees a big change
in your son Joseph.

10:45.862 --> 10:49.030
Yeah, he lashes out
at my wife for no reason.

10:49.032 --> 10:53.268
He physically attacks my other
children for no reason.

10:53.270 --> 10:54.869
Look, I know
teenagers are jerks.

10:54.871 --> 10:57.305
- Couldn't it just be that?
- No.

10:57.307 --> 10:58.940
I mean, he'll have, like,

10:58.942 --> 11:01.076
a glassy but crazy, you know,
look in his eye,

11:01.078 --> 11:04.345
almost like it's not my son.

11:04.347 --> 11:06.614
He has, like, an evil smile.

11:06.616 --> 11:08.216
I hate to say my son
was possessed,

11:08.218 --> 11:10.151
but, I mean, it almost
gave me that impression.

11:10.153 --> 11:11.419
I mean,
what do you think is here?

11:11.421 --> 11:15.123
I don't know if it's demonic,
but I just want it gone.

11:19.896 --> 11:21.663
I'm feeling a paralysis thing.

11:23.734 --> 11:26.234
Somebody having
that happen to them.

11:26.236 --> 11:28.570
Can't move, can't move.

11:28.572 --> 11:30.304
Boy.

11:30.306 --> 11:33.842
I'm seeing these small
black shadow things.

11:33.844 --> 11:35.777
Do you have any idea yet
what these things are?

11:35.779 --> 11:38.113
I think they're, like,
some kind of demonic thing.

11:40.517 --> 11:43.184
These evil little things
are in here.

11:43.186 --> 11:46.521
They are trying to take over

11:46.523 --> 11:50.658
because the evil is <i> in</i> them.

11:50.660 --> 11:53.495
What going on?

11:54.731 --> 11:57.131
Something just hurt me.

11:57.133 --> 11:59.000
Felt like I got jabbed.

12:07.077 --> 12:08.609
Joe, I was talking to
your mom and dad,

12:08.611 --> 12:11.545
and they think that whatever's
going on in this house

12:11.547 --> 12:13.081
is changing your personality.

12:13.083 --> 12:15.216
Yeah, I would agree
with that.

12:15.218 --> 12:17.418
I get mad at everybody
all the time,

12:17.420 --> 12:19.687
ridiculous little things
that happen.

12:19.689 --> 12:21.790
When I'm out of the house,
I feel like, you know,

12:21.792 --> 12:24.425
nothing bothers me.
But when I'm in here,

12:24.427 --> 12:27.495
someone could just do
something so insignificant,

12:27.497 --> 12:29.297
and I'd just lose it.

12:29.299 --> 12:31.365
All right, so what about
experiences that you've had?

12:31.367 --> 12:34.035
For 15 years,
I've seen shadow figures.

12:34.037 --> 12:35.136
What do they look like
to you?

12:35.138 --> 12:38.306
Some have, like,
oddly shaped heads,

12:38.308 --> 12:41.409
oddly shaped bodies,
tentacle-like arms.

12:41.411 --> 12:44.579
That's a new one.
Anything else going on with you?

12:44.581 --> 12:47.982
Well, I have these
vivid nightmares constantly.

12:47.984 --> 12:49.717
Do me a favor
and describe one for me.

12:49.719 --> 12:51.452
Sometimes I just wake up,

12:51.454 --> 12:52.854
and something's
trying to get me.

12:52.856 --> 12:54.322
All right, so this thing
that's trying to get you

12:54.324 --> 12:55.356
in your dream,
what does it look like?

12:55.358 --> 12:56.591
Can you describe it?

12:56.593 --> 12:57.759
I don't know if
it's a demon or not,

12:57.761 --> 13:00.461
but it sure as hell
looks like one.

13:00.463 --> 13:01.662
Anything else?

13:01.664 --> 13:04.632
I've woken up with
scratches and bruises

13:04.634 --> 13:06.334
on my back and my arms.

13:06.336 --> 13:09.204
Okay, so what are these
scratches like? Are they...

13:09.206 --> 13:11.072
They're not deep,
but they're very visible.

13:11.074 --> 13:12.807
Okay, you're the oldest.

13:12.809 --> 13:14.075
I mean, you got
younger brothers and sisters.

13:14.077 --> 13:16.010
Yeah.
You worried about
your brothers?

13:16.012 --> 13:18.746
I am very worried about them,

13:18.748 --> 13:21.081
and I'm very concerned
about my sister

13:21.083 --> 13:22.517
because of how young she is.

13:22.519 --> 13:24.285
Um...

13:24.287 --> 13:27.856
Sorry. I don't wanna see her
be affected in the future.

13:30.961 --> 13:34.529
Someone here
might be getting influenced.

13:34.531 --> 13:37.031
These things wanna, like,
take over.

13:37.033 --> 13:38.766
Like, it's not, like,
influenced subtly.

13:38.768 --> 13:40.702
No, no, no, it's change.

13:40.704 --> 13:42.203
Like, change.

13:44.174 --> 13:46.073
What do you mean?

13:46.075 --> 13:48.509
I think a personality change.

13:48.511 --> 13:49.977
I think maybe the living
are thinking,

13:49.979 --> 13:51.513
like, this is nightmares.

13:53.250 --> 13:55.483
Is it specifically
the person in this room?

13:56.653 --> 13:57.919
So what do they want
with this kid?

13:57.921 --> 14:01.456
They would like
to take over the kid.

14:10.200 --> 14:12.400
Samantha, how old are you?

14:12.402 --> 14:14.402
- Um, 6.
-6. Okay.

14:14.404 --> 14:16.204
So I was talking
to Mommy today,

14:16.206 --> 14:17.672
and she was telling me
there's some scary things

14:17.674 --> 14:19.641
going on in this house.

14:19.643 --> 14:21.609
Can you tell me about
anything that you've seen

14:21.611 --> 14:22.877
that might have scared you?

14:22.879 --> 14:27.081
I saw, like, shadows
and stuff around the house.

14:27.083 --> 14:28.882
Can you tell me
what those shadow things

14:28.884 --> 14:30.351
looked like to you?

14:30.353 --> 14:33.687
Like, they're, like,
um, on the wall.

14:33.689 --> 14:35.223
They're, like, all black.

14:35.225 --> 14:37.491
And then one of them,
like, leaves.

14:37.493 --> 14:38.826
Like, they disappear.

14:38.828 --> 14:40.761
Okay, anything else
scare you?

14:40.763 --> 14:42.597
I saw a ghost bear.

14:44.000 --> 14:45.633
How big was he?

14:45.635 --> 14:49.069
He was, like,
up to the table.

