28:30.642 --> 28:32.342
Now a woman named Bertie Wells
lived on

28:32.344 --> 28:33.944
the property next door
to that farm

28:33.946 --> 28:35.112
with her husband and two sons.

28:35.114 --> 28:38.615
So now on the evening
of October 5, 1937,

28:38.617 --> 28:40.350
Bertie took
her 3-year-old kid, John,

28:40.352 --> 28:41.785
