- Wow.
- I see him in the back.

29:47.886 --> 29:50.653
He just stands there
and watches you.

29:50.655 --> 29:51.921
Yeah.

29:51.923 --> 29:54.224
He, like,
does not stop moving

29:54.226 --> 29:55.959
And he, because of that,

29:55.961 --> 29:59.096
can affect, like,
the electricity in the house

29:59.098 --> 30:02.365
or, like, TVs and stuff
like that, you know?

30:02.367 --> 30:04.434
Gary, tell her what's going on
with the electric.

30:04.436 --> 30:06.036
We leave the house,
everything was off.

30:06.038 --> 30:08.238
We'd come home, the lights
in the attic are on,

30:08.240 --> 30:11.508
there's TVs on, radios on.
I mean, you name it.

30:11.510 --> 30:13.443
Wow. Okay.

30:13.445 --> 30:15.679
You might, when you're
around him,

30:15.681 --> 30:18.515
feel a lot
of emotional swings.

30:20.119 --> 30:23.553
It's just a constant
struggle for me to be --

30:23.555 --> 30:25.388
just to be happy
with anything.

30:25.390 --> 30:27.657
You know, it's changing
my personality.

30:27.659 --> 30:30.928
I can leave work in a great mood
and I'll walk into the house,

30:30.930 --> 30:33.730
and all of a sudden,
I'm just angry at everybody.

30:33.732 --> 30:35.332
He can make you
feel anxious

30:35.334 --> 30:37.934
and dizzy and nauseous
and drained.

30:37.936 --> 30:40.537
My energy is gone.

30:40.539 --> 30:43.673
I can sleep all day and still
feel like I haven't slept.

30:43.675 --> 30:45.008
It's terrible.

30:45.010 --> 30:46.210
She talked about something else
that we didn't hit on,

30:46.212 --> 30:48.145
was the anxiety, being anxious.

30:48.147 --> 30:50.480
The anxiety,
the panic attacks,

30:50.482 --> 30:53.083
as each month goes by,
it gets worse and worse.

30:53.085 --> 30:54.517
They tried putting me
on meds for it.

30:54.519 --> 30:56.620
Nothing works.

30:56.622 --> 30:57.954
Now all that stuff
they talked about

30:57.956 --> 30:59.422
sounds like
it could be this guy.

30:59.424 --> 31:02.125
Yes, that's that guy.

31:02.127 --> 31:05.229
Get any idea who this guy might
have been when he was alive?

31:05.231 --> 31:07.163
Due to the fact that
he wouldn't stop moving,

31:07.165 --> 31:10.133
I could not really
see him very well,

31:10.135 --> 31:12.902
but I'm thinking
about 30 years of age.

31:12.904 --> 31:16.039
But mentally,
he absolutely seemed like

31:16.041 --> 31:19.509
he was functioning
at a much younger level.

31:19.511 --> 31:23.480
I think that he might have had
some mental illness as well.

31:23.482 --> 31:25.748
Definitely was not in
a good place when he died.

31:25.750 --> 31:29.252
Also, there's
a deceased female who's here,

31:29.254 --> 31:31.321
and there's some kind
of strange connection

31:31.323 --> 31:34.825
between them,
and I'm not sure what.

31:34.827 --> 31:37.327
Well, you know,
I got a pretty good idea

31:37.329 --> 31:39.596
of who this guy might have been,

31:39.598 --> 31:41.197
but I want to wait
until you tell us

31:41.199 --> 31:43.133
about the woman you said
he was connected to.

31:43.135 --> 31:47.203
So she's the most dominant
dead person here.

31:47.205 --> 31:49.405
Got that she was in
her 40s or 50s.

31:49.407 --> 31:51.941
I got that she was
from another country,

31:51.943 --> 31:53.477
but I'm not sure where.

31:53.479 --> 31:56.579
She's extremely religious
person.

31:56.581 --> 31:58.215
<i>Extremely.</i>

31:58.217 --> 32:00.484
Got that she was married,

32:00.486 --> 32:02.819
ended up losing
all her money somehow.

32:02.821 --> 32:05.422
And then
it got worse for her

32:05.424 --> 32:07.691
because then
her husband died,

32:07.693 --> 32:10.394
and apparently,
it was a horrible death.

32:10.396 --> 32:15.098
After he died, that was it.
Boom. Everything went to...

32:15.100 --> 32:16.900
Now I know who
you're talking about.

32:16.902 --> 32:19.770
So in the 1890s,
there was a European couple

32:19.772 --> 32:21.971
that lived in a cottage
right next to this property.

32:21.973 --> 32:25.375
Now this guy was part of
the Hungarian royal family.

32:25.377 --> 32:26.877
His name was Rudolf Palffy.

32:26.879 --> 32:28.679
Now the expert
I talked to told me

32:28.681 --> 32:30.714
that Rudolf and his brother
were pretty immature.

32:30.716 --> 32:33.649
They basically partied
and spent the father's fortune.

32:33.651 --> 32:35.985
The father went bankrupt
in 1873.

32:35.987 --> 32:38.121
Now the father was so ashamed
by what happened,

32:38.123 --> 32:40.924
he shot and killed himself
a few years later.

32:40.926 --> 32:43.860
Rudolf then went to go live
with his brother, Arthur,

32:43.862 --> 32:46.430
hoping to, you know,
get money off of him,

32:46.432 --> 32:47.931
but he was living in France.

32:47.933 --> 32:50.734
Arthur winds up shooting himself
in the head in 1889

32:50.736 --> 32:51.902
and killing himself.

32:54.072 --> 32:56.406
After Arthur's suicide,
Rudolf married

32:56.408 --> 32:59.176
his dead brother's girlfriend,
Rosalia Zimmerman.

32:59.178 --> 33:01.277
Rudolf's family was pissed
about the marriage

33:01.279 --> 33:02.545
for a couple of reasons.

33:02.547 --> 33:04.147
First, he was royalty,
and she wasn't.

33:04.149 --> 33:06.015
So the other issue
they had with the marriage

33:06.017 --> 33:09.186
was that family was Catholic,
and she was Jewish.

33:09.188 --> 33:11.355
The expert I talked to said
they wanted a fresh start

33:11.357 --> 33:13.290
and they came to America
from France.

33:13.292 --> 33:14.724
When they did come here, though,

33:14.726 --> 33:17.728
he had the equivalent of what
would have been $140,000,

33:17.730 --> 33:20.263
and he went through it
within a year.

33:20.265 --> 33:22.966
In 1893,
Rudolf goes out drinking

33:22.968 --> 33:24.700
with some of the locals in town.

33:24.702 --> 33:27.170
When he gets home, him and
Rosalia got into a huge fight.

33:27.172 --> 33:29.573
The two were arguing
when he stopped, he said,

33:29.575 --> 33:30.707
"I love you dearly,

33:30.709 --> 33:32.642
but Switzerland cannot
rule Hungary,"

33:32.644 --> 33:35.412
pulls out a pistol
and blows his brains out.

33:37.383 --> 33:39.216
And he did it
right in front of her.

33:40.386 --> 33:42.185
Now you said he was about 30?

33:42.187 --> 33:44.487
He was 32 when he died.

33:44.489 --> 33:46.156
So do you think
this is who you saw?

33:46.158 --> 33:47.524
Yes.

33:47.526 --> 33:50.860
Now you said the dead woman,
his wife, was dominant.

33:50.862 --> 33:53.263
Yeah. She's just bad news.

33:53.265 --> 33:56.933
She's extremely protective
of this house and the land.

33:58.137 --> 34:00.269
She's extremely angry
at the living here,

34:00.271 --> 34:02.138
and one of the things
I saw her doing

34:02.140 --> 34:05.608
was sharpening her fingernails
and scratching living people.

34:05.610 --> 34:09.344
Jen, the scratches,
you and Joseph.

34:09.347 --> 34:13.283
Scratches, bruises,
both me and the 15-year-old.

34:13.284 --> 34:15.152
They seem to come up
in the middle of the night

34:15.154 --> 34:18.221
or just show up out of nowhere.
- Interesting.

34:18.223 --> 34:20.190
The other thing was
that she had died from

34:20.192 --> 34:22.725
some kind of infections,
and now when

34:22.726 --> 34:26.396
she's around living people,
she can make you feel like that.

34:26.398 --> 34:28.331
And I was concerned
about people here

34:28.333 --> 34:31.234
developing random illnesses.

34:31.235 --> 34:34.170
They say I have, like,
reversed immune system,

34:34.172 --> 34:35.839
and they gave me
antibiotics.

34:35.841 --> 34:37.940
I have to take, like,
three, four rounds of it

34:37.943 --> 34:40.842
before anything works.
- Every time she gets a cold,

34:40.844 --> 34:43.179
it almost always
turns into pneumonia.

34:43.181 --> 34:45.547
Now could all of this be
this woman?

34:45.550 --> 34:47.583
Yes.

34:47.585 --> 34:50.920
I saw her in the blue
bedroom upstairs.

34:50.922 --> 34:52.755
That's Joseph's room, right?

34:52.757 --> 34:54.324
I did have a sketch done.

35:00.999 --> 35:02.265
Ooh.

35:08.606 --> 35:10.340
Okay.

35:19.218 --> 35:21.384
Believe me now?

35:21.386 --> 35:22.785
What is she doing to him?

35:22.787 --> 35:24.855
Strangling him.

35:27.359 --> 35:29.159
- I know it's tough to look at.
- Yeah, I-I can't.

35:29.161 --> 35:30.493
Here, we'll just turn it over.

35:35.434 --> 35:36.900
I hate to even ask
what else.

35:36.902 --> 35:41.171
There's something here that
has me much more concerned.

35:41.173 --> 35:42.973
- More than this?
- Yeah.

35:42.975 --> 35:46.375
There were these entities
that I saw during my walk.

35:46.377 --> 35:49.112
They looked like
small shadow figures

35:49.114 --> 35:52.048
or small -- They almost
looked like ghosts.

35:52.050 --> 35:53.884
Like if somebody had a child,

35:53.886 --> 35:57.386
dropped a black sheet
on the child...

35:57.388 --> 35:59.523
I've seen them everywhere
around, through the house.

35:59.525 --> 36:01.390
Little kid
with like, you know,

36:01.392 --> 36:04.427
just like you're putting,
like, a blanket over him.

36:05.931 --> 36:07.597
They do make people sick.

36:07.599 --> 36:09.999
When I came into contact
with them upstairs

36:10.001 --> 36:12.602
in the blue room,
I felt like the person,

36:12.604 --> 36:14.070
the living person in there,

36:14.072 --> 36:17.140
would have bouts of
severe nausea

36:17.142 --> 36:18.874
if not vomiting.

36:18.876 --> 36:22.111
So have you guys noticed
anything like that with Joe?

36:22.113 --> 36:24.847
Yes, he comes downstairs
and he's like,

36:24.849 --> 36:26.082
"Can I get an container
or something?

36:26.084 --> 36:27.383
I feel like I'm gonna throw up."

36:27.385 --> 36:30.153
Okay, living people here
would believe

36:30.155 --> 36:31.888
that they're having
nightmares,

36:31.890 --> 36:35.958
but it would be due to
these things influencing them.

36:35.960 --> 36:37.927
When I talk to Joe,
he told me he has

36:37.929 --> 36:40.096
constant nightmares about
a demon attacking him.

36:40.098 --> 36:42.498
He's had these nightmares
for as long as he can remember.

36:42.500 --> 36:45.101
These things also
manipulate the living

36:45.103 --> 36:46.302
when they're awake.

36:46.304 --> 36:49.506
I saw this little child,
and his personality

36:49.508 --> 36:52.842
completely changes,
and it just gave me chills

36:52.844 --> 36:54.945
seeing this vision
because it was like,

36:54.947 --> 36:58.114
you knew, like, this wasn't
this kid anymore.

36:58.116 --> 37:00.850
I mean, that's one of
our big things with Joe.

37:00.852 --> 37:02.919
Sometimes I feel like
he's not there.

37:02.921 --> 37:04.787
I don't want to use
the word "possessed,"

37:04.789 --> 37:07.457
but it's the feeling
that I get.

37:07.459 --> 37:11.260
I had a sketch done of what
I saw in the blue bedroom.

37:18.536 --> 37:21.671
I- I gotta show it to you,
even though I don't wanna.

37:21.673 --> 37:24.007
My God.

37:24.009 --> 37:26.543
I don't know what to say.

37:32.718 --> 37:35.084
What the hell are
these things?

37:35.086 --> 37:38.855
I believe that they are
a type of demonic entity.

37:41.159 --> 37:43.593
They're very bad.

37:43.595 --> 37:46.229
Well, what about Joseph?
What do they want from him?

37:46.231 --> 37:47.464
They want to possess him.

37:50.035 --> 37:51.500
And I'm always afraid
of Joseph doing

37:51.502 --> 37:54.537
something to hurt himself
or somebody else.

37:54.539 --> 37:57.774
I also saw these things
in the room across the hall.

37:57.776 --> 37:59.775
- Samantha's?
- Samantha's room.

37:59.777 --> 38:03.079
They already had her,
like, from birth.

38:03.081 --> 38:05.715
That's why the activity's
gotten worse.

38:05.717 --> 38:09.452
My God.

38:09.454 --> 38:11.354
- Is she possessed?
- Yeah.

38:11.356 --> 38:14.223
My God.

38:14.225 --> 38:16.926
There's one that's literally
inside her all the time.

38:36.181 --> 38:37.580
So, Jen, you called us in

38:37.582 --> 38:39.615
because you thought the kids
were in danger here.

38:39.617 --> 38:42.985
And I don't know if it was
mother's intuition or what,

38:42.987 --> 38:46.289
but based on what Amy's
told us, you are 100% right.

38:46.291 --> 38:48.191
So now the big question is,

38:48.193 --> 38:51.127
is there a way for you
to save your children,

38:51.129 --> 38:53.329
or do you need to pack up
before someone

38:53.331 --> 38:55.965
gets seriously hurt
and get the hell out of here?

38:55.967 --> 38:58.468
For that answer,
I'm gonna turn it over to Amy.

39:00.272 --> 39:03.539
So, we're going to start
with the dead man.

39:03.541 --> 39:05.541
Talking about Rudolf,
the guy who shot himself?

39:05.543 --> 39:06.809
Right.

39:06.811 --> 39:08.677
So getting him
out of the house,

39:08.679 --> 39:11.948
we're going to utilize
tar water.

39:11.950 --> 39:17.087
The tar water forms
a long-lasting barrier

39:17.089 --> 39:21.757
that prevents the dead
from entering your home.

39:21.759 --> 39:24.627
You're also going to be
removing the dead lady.

39:24.629 --> 39:27.730
You mean Rudolf's wife, Rosalia?
Yes.

39:27.732 --> 39:30.600
This one, you're going
to need a medium for.

39:30.602 --> 39:34.604
Someone who is Jewish,
who is also a medium,

39:34.606 --> 39:37.207
who can come and talk to her

39:37.209 --> 39:41.644
and specifically tell her
that she's gotta go.

39:41.646 --> 39:43.880
She's gonna move on
real quick.

39:45.050 --> 39:48.284
Now as far as the demons,

39:48.286 --> 39:50.686
you do need
to set up an exorcism

39:50.688 --> 39:52.956
to take place for Sam.

39:55.827 --> 39:57.426
It could be very traumatic

39:57.428 --> 40:01.097
and this could take
several meetings.

40:01.099 --> 40:03.566
I'm already dreading
just the fact to have to

40:03.568 --> 40:04.967
try to somehow
explain it to her,

40:04.969 --> 40:06.469
let alone put her through it.

40:06.471 --> 40:09.839
It's not like she necessarily
has to be told these things.

40:09.841 --> 40:11.908
For all she knows,
he's just doing

40:11.910 --> 40:13.609
- nice little prayers over her.
- Yeah.

40:13.611 --> 40:15.912
So you're saying exorcism
for Sam.
Yes.

40:15.914 --> 40:17.246
What about Joseph?

40:17.248 --> 40:20.483
After Sam, then Joseph.

40:20.485 --> 40:22.352
How do you think Joseph's
going to react to this?

40:22.354 --> 40:24.253
I think he's gonna
feel vindicated

40:24.255 --> 40:26.856
and embrace the fight
to get it taken care of.

40:28.693 --> 40:32.395
Okay, once both of the children
have been taken care of,

40:32.397 --> 40:34.630
then the entire house
has to be blessed

40:34.632 --> 40:35.899
as well as the land.

40:35.901 --> 40:37.166
And then every year,

40:37.168 --> 40:39.936
you have to have the house
and the land blessed.

40:39.938 --> 40:42.338
So the exorcism
and then blessing the house

40:42.340 --> 40:43.806
will get rid
of the little demons?

40:43.808 --> 40:45.708
Correct.

40:45.710 --> 40:48.677
And so what about their mood
swings and personality changes?

40:48.679 --> 40:50.146
Will those get better, too?

40:50.148 --> 40:53.149
Once they're completely done
with absolutely everything,

40:53.151 --> 40:55.051
yeah, it'll be good.

40:55.053 --> 40:56.385
It's funny, when we talked,

40:56.387 --> 40:58.354
you broke my heart actually,
listening to you.

40:58.356 --> 40:59.722
All you wanted was
your kids to be safe

40:59.724 --> 41:01.191
and to save your marriage.

41:01.193 --> 41:04.828
Now she basically gave you
a map on how to do that.

41:04.830 --> 41:07.697
So are you going to do
what Amy tells you to do?

41:07.699 --> 41:08.832
Absolutely.

41:08.834 --> 41:11.467
There's not a question
in my mind.

41:11.469 --> 41:13.336
I can't thank you enough...

41:15.974 --> 41:18.908
'cause it's gotta stop now.

41:29.187 --> 41:31.454
It won't be easy
removing the dead

41:31.456 --> 41:32.855
in Jen and Gary's home,

41:32.857 --> 41:35.658
but with the help
of a medium and tar water,

41:35.660 --> 41:37.960
they can be banished.

41:37.962 --> 41:41.664
If they do that and get
Sam and Joe exercised,

41:41.666 --> 41:45.167
this family will find the peace
they've been searching for.

